title: Im still banned?
body: Ok so i got banned until the november 28 at 3:24 pm and its 3:34 and im still banned why is that?

replies.body: It doesn't look like this account is banned or suspended at all. Were you talking about a different account? If not you most likely just had a little time left until the ban was lifted.
it was with my different account and yes i had to give it an hour before it worked thank you for your response.
Whats the Summoner name for the other account? I can go ahead and look into it for ya!
